: Chota Nagpur: Nawatoli (
<bibRefCitation id="EFC34B65FFFD775B4E67F9C631A3F8B4" author="Maindron, M." box="[1038,1218,1643,1670]" pageId="5" pageNumber="70" pagination="130 - 131" refId="ref20275" refString="Maindron, M. (1898) Description de deux especes nouvelles de Carabiques de l'Inde orientale. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 1898, 130 - 131." type="journal article" year="1898">Maindron 1898</bibRefCitation>
